      <!-- PAGE -->

      <div class="page">

        <div class="container">
          <div class="eight columns about">
            <h1>The Legacy of Hope</h1>
            <p>The Legacy of Hope Foundation provides medical care and facilities for underserved children and communities around the world. In that spirit, please join us in our global campaign to fulfill the last living wish of Nelson Mandela—to help build the Nelson Mandela Children’s Hospital.</p>
